.TH NOTEPAD 1 "March 2025" "bas+ 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
notepad \- simple graphical notepad
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B notepad
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B notepad
is a minimal graphical text editor built with the bas+ UI architecture
(menubar/toolbar from action/group models).
.PP
It provides File (New, Open, Save, Save As, Exit) and Edit (Cut, Copy, Paste)
menus and a toolbar.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR bas+ (1)
